  This is a 2d platforming game! It currently features multiple levels from 5
  original worlds. It also contains a bonus level. The game will be updated
  from time to time with free dlc content and new levels! You explore the
  world collecting gems to save your friends and family. Try to earn high
  scores by collecting as many coins and gems as you can! Do you have the
  platforming skill it takes to become the best gem collector ever?

  Plot Summary.
  There are twelve tribes in the Ashne Kingdom. Each year, a different tribe
  is required to bring forth a "collection" to the mad King Dinglah who rules
  the land. If the collection is not met, he will send out forces to destroy
  the entire tribe. Nomi, a creature from the nomadic earth tribe has
  volunteered in this year's collection in order to protect his friends and
  family.
